                    <figure>
                        <figDesc>8 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                        <p>8Â¢ U.S. AIR MAIL</p>
                    </figure>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. Lucile Aly</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>1138 22nd Ave., East,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Eugene,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Oregon.</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </ab>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.40.3-5_0003b"/>
                
                <note type="authorial"><p>I happened on the Jones letter. <del/> Please put it with those Mona collected.</p> 
                    
                <p>My books are gone. Two men worked two days packing and handling. It's empty here, but I'm making the empty room beautiful.</p> Jno.</note>
                
                
                
